          <title>Texans get 2 points on blocked extra point return vs. Chargers, 1st in NFL playoff history</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Houston's D'Angelo Ross returned a blocked extra point for two points in the fourth quarter of the Texans' wild-card playoff victory over the Los Angeles Chargers on Saturday — the first such play in NFL postseason history.]]></description>
